{"tid":417875,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"荷里活翻拍日本動畫《你的名字。》真人版","createTime":"2017-09-29T05:49:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T22:31:55.000Z","uid":14788,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d5738aa232ae19b196d33dc66e82a6654b208786","tid":417875,"uid":14788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170928/mobile/bkn-20170928094919605-0928_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170928%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170928094919605-0928_00862_001.html&d=r8vLENpNF1Mbh9U0VN3FY5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=da3562af\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170928/mobile/bkn-20170928094919605-0928_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本動畫家新海誠去年編導的口碑動畫《你的名字。》叫好叫座，全球票房大收約27.7億港元，派拉蒙電影公司近日被爆已買下改編權，將與日本東寶電影公司合作會開拍真人版電影！電影將由《天煞異降》（Arrival）編劇Eric Heisserer寫劇本，《星空奇遇記》（Star Trek）名導JJ阿伯拉罕（J.J Abrams）以及動畫監製川村元氣亦將參與製作工作，至於粉絲最關注的幕前卡士現時就仍未公布！ <br />\n<br />\n對於《你的名字。》被拍成荷里活真人版，新海誠都有回應，表示對電影寄予期待，又謂原作是基於生活在日本的本土想像力以及國內技術而創造的，作品與荷里活產生交集後，可能會帶來新的可能性！ <br />\n<br />\n荷里活近年主力有迪士尼將經典動畫拍成真人電影，《美女與野獸》（Beauty And the Beast）與《阿拉丁》（Aladdin）等都令粉絲大為期待，派拉蒙今次將日本大熱動畫拍成荷里活真人版，相信會令不少原版粉絲關注！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975453381a45d3290fc203ccb7c09dc3bdad6eb0","tid":417875,"uid":8727,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T05:51:09.000Z","msg":"唔好啦"},{"pid":"15ee67c500ba434a147b108b5eea7bec1fc53764","tid":417875,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89c23ed23a2d162956c17063467125c6ca797e5","tid":417875,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T07:01:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得實好爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4